<br>
I've seen a lot of posts lately about wiz spells dropping in PoG. I've recorded the following:<br>
<br>
Spells dropped in PoG:<br>
<br>
Translocate<br>
Improved Invs<br>
GD Portal<br>
CS Portal<br>
Solists Ice Spear<br>
<br>
Now, being an Agnostic wizard I am welcome in PoG. My question is a survey of what you all think, I can get in on PoG raids with friends I know, But, I am not sure if I am ready to ruin my faction there, afterall..I'm stil waiting to see what quest the totem guy gives.<br>
<br>
What do you all think I should do? Keep the faction and wait and see what happens or just destroy it with in turn getting my spells.<br>
<br>
Thanks for the input,<br>
<br>
53 wizard<br>
Xegony <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#33333><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/udaeanorendarion.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Daeanor Endarion</A>&nbsp; <IMG SRC=http://www.monmouth.com/~dhawthorne/everqst/picon.gif BORDER=0 WIDTH=10 HEIGHT=10></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Wizard</span><br> <font color=#ffffff>(1/14/01 5:03:18 am)</font><br>    <BR><img src=http://www.monmouth.com/~dhawthorne/everqst/ppic.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Awww, and I wanted to keep my PoG faction. </span><hr size=1> If your faction is good there, zone in and auction you want to buy. Might get lucky. I got GD portal by auctioning...paid 400pp and a ride to DL for it. Heh, matter of fact, I think I'll load up a few k and try this myself. <p><b>Daeanor Endarion of the Rathe</b></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub23.ezboard.com/udmitrythewizzy.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Dmitry the Wizzy</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Apprentice</span><br> <font color=#ffffff>(1/16/01 7:24:40 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> The Dark Side</span><hr size=1> I am agnostic too.  I am pretty sure I am gonna miss out on some quests by killing in PoG but MANNNNNN this is a FUN zone.  If you have access to people who all want to come here (ie the better part of my guild) then it has advantages to blow your faction.  <br>
<br>
The armor is great stuff.<br>
Our bloody spells actually drop here.<br>
It is like a roving fear with smaller number of people and no millions of deaths on break.<br>
<br>
For me, I made the sacrifice to keep Dragon faction.  THat makes cobolt scar and waking lands portal usable.  I said the hell with it and destroyed my PoG factions.<br>
<br>
Dmitry 54 Wizzy<br>
